Security in the cloud  Your responsibility includes the following areas.


The security configuration of the data plane, including the configuration of the security groups that allow traffic to pass from the Alibaba Cloud ACK control plane into the customer VPC;

The configuration of the worker nodes and the containers themselves;

The worker node guest operating system (including updates and security patches);




Other associated application software:


Setting up and managing network controls, such as firewall rules

Managing platform-level identity and access management
